\[*Call for Speakers*\] I am organizing a session on ``Healthcare Service Planning'' in Cluster ``Healthcare Management'' at [https://dev.ifors2023.com/ IFORS 2023]. Any topic in planning for healthcare service, be it strategic or operational, that can be tackled by mathematical programming is welcome. Please contact me if you are interested. Alternatively, you can submit your abstract directly by clicking [https://www.euro-online.org/conf/ifors2023/ here] and using the code 1777b464.
